; Regression test for issue #725: Output of cleared not aligned with --date-format
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/725
; When --date-format produces dates wider than the default, the cleared
; command's separator dashes and blank-date placeholders must match.

2024/01/01 * Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Hardware Store
    Expenses:Tools    $25.00
    Assets:Cash

test cleared --date-format '%Y-%m-%d'
         $-35.00             $-10.00    2024-01-01    Assets:Cash
          $35.00              $10.00                 Expenses
          $10.00              $10.00    2024-01-01      Food
          $25.00                   0                   Tools
----------------  ------------------    ---------
               0                   0             
end test
